captions.translation: [JIUTAI] Now I petition: It is not for the glory of my name: Munechika,
but at the imperial command of the Emperor,
captions.transcription: Munechika watakushi no kōmyō ni arazu,

captions.translation: whose rule extends from heaven to earth, that I call on all divine beings,
numberless as the sand of the Ganges,
to join your strength now with Munechika.
captions.transcription: tadaima no Munechika ni chikara wo awasete tabitamae tote.

captions.translation: I offer up this sacred wand.
I bow my head before heaven as I seek divine aid from my inmost being.
captions.transcription: Ten ni aogi kōbe ō katamuke kot'nzui no tansei kiki-ire.
